{
  "title": "01 \u2014 Service Health: playout",
  "uid": "stream-health-playout",
  "tags": [
    "tripbot",
    "playout",
    "mediamtx",
    "stream"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "platform",
        "label": "Platform",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
        },
        "query": "label_values(playout_pipeline_running_time_ms{service_name=\"playout\"}, service_platform)",
        "current": {
          "text": "twitch",
          "value": "twitch"
        },
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": false,
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "deployment_environment",
        "label": "Environment (playout only)",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
        },
        "query": "label_values(playout_pipeline_running_time_ms{service_name=\"playout\"}, deployment_environment)",
        "current": {
          "text": "prod-1",
          "value": "prod-1"
        },
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": false,
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 300,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "NATS control plane",
      "description": "1 = this service's NATS connection is up; 0 = down, so its playback commands / live events are being dropped even though the process is running. Catches the boot-race where a consumer starts before NATS is reachable and stays deaf until restart. Aggregated across platform instances (min: red if any is down). No data reads as disconnected.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "min by (deployment_environment) (playout_nats_connected{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "NATS DISCONNECTED",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "NATS connected",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "noValue": "0"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 57,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "The dashcam publish path: **playout** (GStreamer/Rust) encodes one gapless H.264 stream and publishes it into the per-platform **MediaMTX** relay, which OBS reads.\n\n- **Playout row** \u2014 `playout_*` OTLP-push metrics, filtered by `service_platform=$platform` and `deployment_environment=$deployment_environment`. Push arrives from **both stage-1 and prod-1**.\n- **MediaMTX row** \u2014 annotation-scraped from the relay pods (`pod=~\"mediamtx-$platform.*\"`); the `$deployment_environment` variable does **not** apply. Only **prod-1** ships (stage-1 is dropped at the Alloy layer), so these panels stay empty for stage.\n\nOnly `playout-youtube` exists pre-cutover \u2014 `twitch` panels populate once the twitch playout is live."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Playout (publisher)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Data fresh (last 1m)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(time() - max(timestamp(last_over_time(playout_pipeline_running_time_ms{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[10m])))) < bool 60"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "STALE",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "FRESH",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Realtime health (s/s)",
      "description": "Pipeline running time advancing per wallclock second. ~1.0 = holding realtime; a sustained dip means the encoder is falling behind (the wedge tell).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "deriv(playout_pipeline_running_time_ms{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[5m]) / 1000"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 2,
          "unit": "none",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.9
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.97
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Clip spawns / min",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(playout_clip_spawns_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 60"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 1,
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Running version",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 18,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "group by (service_version) (playout_pipeline_running_time_ms{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_version}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "none",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "name",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Realtime health over time (s/s)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "deriv(playout_pipeline_running_time_ms{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[5m]) / 1000",
          "legendFormat": "[{{deployment_environment}} / {{service_platform}}]"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "none",
          "decimals": 2,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.97
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Playhead position in active clip",
      "description": "Position within the currently-playing clip. Sawtooth: climbs, resets to 0 at each clip boundary.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "playout_playhead_position_ms{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"} / 1000",
          "legendFormat": "[{{deployment_environment}} / {{service_platform}}]"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Commands / sec by verb",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (verb) (rate(playout_commands_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{verb}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Clip spawns / min",
      "description": "Clips spliced into the pipeline (boundaries + redirect commands). A steady baseline \u2248 one clip length; spikes signal churn or a redirect storm.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 16,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(playout_clip_spawns_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "[{{deployment_environment}} / {{service_platform}}]"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 1,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Output fps",
      "description": "Frames leaving the pipeline per second at the output tee. The corpus is 1080p60, so this should sit at 60; a sustained dip is the stream actually dropping frames (CPU contention or a stalled encoder).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 24,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_platform, deployment_environment) (rate(playout_output_frames_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval]))"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 1,
          "unit": "none",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 55
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 59
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Frame gaps / min",
      "description": "Output frames whose PTS jumped past 1.5 frame intervals \u2014 visible stalls or dropped frames. concat keeps running time continuous across splices, so a gap is a real hitch, not a clip boundary. 0 is healthy.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 24,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_platform, deployment_environment) (rate(playout_output_frame_gaps_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 60"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 1,
          "unit": "none",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.5
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 6
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Clip errors / min",
      "description": "Clip bins torn down after a decode/negotiation error, then recovered. Steady 0 is healthy; a sustained rate means a bad stretch of corpus or a spec-violating clip.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 16,
        "y": 24,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_platform, deployment_environment) (rate(playout_clip_errors_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 60"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 1,
          "unit": "none",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.5
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 3
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Output fps over time",
      "description": "Output frame rate at the tee sink. Should track 60 flat; dips reveal frame drops the MediaMTX relay bitrate can't distinguish from lower-motion scenes.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 28,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_platform, deployment_environment) (rate(playout_output_frames_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "[{{deployment_environment}} / {{service_platform}}]"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "none",
          "decimals": 1,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Frame gaps & clip errors / min",
      "description": "Playout quality faults: PTS gaps (viewer-visible stutter) and clip errors (recovered clip teardowns). Both should baseline at 0.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 28,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_platform, deployment_environment) (rate(playout_output_frame_gaps_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "gaps [{{deployment_environment}} / {{service_platform}}]"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum by (service_platform, deployment_environment) (rate(playout_clip_errors_total{service_name=\"playout\", service_platform=~\"$platform\", deployment_environment=~\"$deployment_environment\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "clip errors [{{deployment_environment}} / {{service_platform}}]"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 1,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 200,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "MediaMTX relay (prod-1 only)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 36,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Path ready",
      "description": "MediaMTX `dashcam` path in the ready state \u2014 a publisher is connected and the relay is serving.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 37,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max(paths{name=\"dashcam\", state=\"ready\", pod=~\"mediamtx-$platform.*\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "NOT READY",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "READY",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "noValue": "NO DATA"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Publisher connected",
      "description": "RTSP sessions publishing to the dashcam path (playout). Expected: 1.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "__DS_PROMETHEUS__"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 37,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rtsp_sessions{path=\"dashcam\", state=\"publish\", pod=~\"mediamtx-$platform.*\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "noValue": "0"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
